      "recommendation": "Option A — strongly recommended. Rename the quote status to 'accepted.' It accurately describes the business event (customer accepted the terms), avoids collision with the established meaning of 'confirmed,' and requires zero changes to existing order logic. The feature request's business need is fully met; only the label changes."
    }
  ],

  "rejection_reasons": [
